<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="significance-n">significance <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sɪɡ'nɪfɪkəns/    美 /sɪɡ'nɪfɪkəns/  </p>
<p>[U] &amp;[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>重要性；(意义) 重大：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To be honest, a lot of people <strong>attach</strong> too much <strong>significance to</strong> becoming rich and famous.
老实说，很多人太看重名和利。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All the members should realize the value and <strong>significance of</strong> what they are going to do.
所有成员都应该认识到他们将要做的事情的价值和重要性。</p><footer>2011 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The discovery of the new drug is <strong>of great significance for</strong> / <strong>to</strong> people suffering from heart problems.
这种新药的发现对心脏病患者来说意义重大。</p></div></div>